WEBVTT

01:20.120 --> 01:21.200
‎LIQUOR

01:26.520 --> 01:27.480
Come!

01:33.520 --> 01:37.000
QINGFENG STRONGHOLD

01:37.080 --> 01:39.280
Young brother, you're awake.

01:40.080 --> 01:40.920
Come.

01:41.000 --> 01:41.680
SECOND BOSS OF QINGFENG STRONGHOLD

01:41.760 --> 01:43.040
Have some drinks.

01:47.600 --> 01:48.560
Damn, she is good.

01:48.640 --> 01:49.480
Bravo!

01:49.560 --> 01:51.040
You're all so weak. Can't take a hit.

01:51.120 --> 01:52.680
That's our big boss.

01:52.760 --> 01:53.880
SHISAN NIANG
BIG BOSS OF QINGFENG STRONGHOLD

01:53.960 --> 01:55.240
Who else refuses to yield?

01:55.760 --> 01:56.480
No one.

01:56.560 --> 01:57.800
You go up. Why don't you go?

01:57.880 --> 01:58.880
I dare not.

01:58.960 --> 02:00.920
You can't beat my sister.

02:01.000 --> 02:01.960
Don't just end up taking a tumble

02:02.040 --> 02:03.440
and losing face.

02:06.040 --> 02:08.600
Do you know why I'm the boss
of Qingfeng Stronghold?

02:09.240 --> 02:10.680
A bunch of stinking men.

02:11.200 --> 02:12.760
All you know is how to bully women.

02:14.520 --> 02:18.400
Who else wants to come up
and have a fight?

02:19.680 --> 02:20.920
-I dare not.
-One-on-one?

02:21.000 --> 02:22.880
Useless bunch of stinking men.

02:23.400 --> 02:24.720
I'm not playing with you anymore.

02:26.840 --> 02:28.560
How about I give it a try?

02:31.920 --> 02:34.520
When we saved you,
you were still unconscious.

02:34.600 --> 02:36.520
Your hand is injured. Don't push yourself.

02:36.600 --> 02:38.240
Go back and rest quickly.

02:39.720 --> 02:42.200
Our Shisan Niang
is not someone to mess with.

02:47.240 --> 02:49.040
Don't try to show off,

02:49.120 --> 02:50.320
if it costs you your life.

02:52.640 --> 02:54.360
I never bully women.

02:54.880 --> 02:55.880
I'll just use one hand.

03:01.080 --> 03:02.840
-Good.
-Good.

03:02.920 --> 03:04.240
-Fight!
-Fight!

03:04.320 --> 03:05.640
-Great!
-Go for it!

03:05.720 --> 03:06.640
-Fight!
-Fight!

03:35.280 --> 03:41.320
-Good!
-Good!

03:41.400 --> 03:46.040
-Bravo!
-Good!

05:29.480 --> 05:34.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:38.560 --> 05:42.080
Help! Bandits are here! Help!

06:07.120 --> 06:08.120
Who are you?

06:09.960 --> 06:11.160
Our lord wants to see you.

06:11.240 --> 06:12.080
Please.

06:24.520 --> 06:25.680
Benefactor,

06:25.760 --> 06:27.720
thank you for saving my life.

06:28.920 --> 06:29.840
Come up.

06:31.240 --> 06:32.840
-Mother!
-Bao'er!

06:32.920 --> 06:34.880
Let go of my mother!

06:38.240 --> 06:39.360
No need to repay later.

06:39.880 --> 06:41.800
Repaying with yourself right now is fine.

06:43.480 --> 06:44.680
Mr. Qi.

06:45.360 --> 06:46.200
It's you.

06:46.800 --> 06:47.640
Yes.

06:50.120 --> 06:52.280
In this world, besides me,

06:53.680 --> 06:55.480
who else would be this good to you?

06:56.000 --> 06:58.760
Who would rush to save you
before the massacre?

07:16.560 --> 07:17.600
This is your reward.

07:29.440 --> 07:31.520
It's… It's you.

07:37.800 --> 07:38.920
Your face… How did it change?

07:39.960 --> 07:41.000
This face…

07:41.520 --> 07:42.360
Is it good?

07:44.520 --> 07:45.560
If I didn't fix this face…

07:48.440 --> 07:50.760
how could I come to see you?

08:10.360 --> 08:12.480
Dare to kill our people?
You're looking for death!

08:13.080 --> 08:15.560
Insolent fool! Do you know
who is in the carriage?

08:16.640 --> 08:17.640
Stop!

08:17.720 --> 08:18.560
Move aside!

08:26.800 --> 08:28.160
‎MASTERY IN BRUSH AND INK

08:28.960 --> 08:30.600
-Brother!
-Brother Qing!

08:31.960 --> 08:33.240
Weren't you going to Lucheng?

08:33.320 --> 08:34.240
What are you doing in Lin'an?

08:35.480 --> 08:37.120
I heard you fell into the river
and went missing.

08:37.200 --> 08:38.440
My heart burned with anxiety.

08:38.520 --> 08:39.720
So I came to find you first.

08:41.200 --> 08:42.200
You're injured.

08:44.400 --> 08:46.160
Minor injury. It's fine.

08:47.360 --> 08:49.640
Brother, you go to Baxia
and wait for me first.

08:49.720 --> 08:51.200
When the time comes,
we'll go to Lucheng together.

08:51.280 --> 08:52.640
Even if Father gets angry,

08:52.720 --> 08:54.040
I can take the heat for you.

08:55.800 --> 08:57.680
Then what about you? Not coming with me?

08:59.640 --> 09:00.880
I spent a fortune

09:00.960 --> 09:03.200
to recruit the entire
Qingfeng Stronghold bandits.

09:03.280 --> 09:05.240
I shall give Marquis Wu'an a nice gift.

09:06.120 --> 09:08.200
They're focusing on Lucheng now.

09:08.840 --> 09:11.760
I will slaughter
all the commoners around here

09:11.840 --> 09:13.560
to make him lose
his reputation completely.

09:14.160 --> 09:16.240
Previously, I planned the buyout of grain.

09:16.320 --> 09:17.400
It was meant to help you.

09:17.920 --> 09:18.960
I never thought

09:19.040 --> 09:20.880
Marquis Wu'an would turn
the scheme against us.

09:21.400 --> 09:22.960
You must be careful in the future.

09:24.160 --> 09:26.040
They all say Marquis Wu'an's
calculations never fail.

09:26.120 --> 09:28.880
Maybe this time, I'll find his weakness.

09:30.600 --> 09:32.480
You learned from Marquis Wu'an
since childhood.

09:32.560 --> 09:33.400
You know yourself and your enemy.

09:34.000 --> 09:35.200
You already surpassed yourself.

09:35.280 --> 09:37.520
You were born to defeat him.

09:39.640 --> 09:40.920
With your unparalleled strategy

09:41.000 --> 09:42.400
and my bravery,

09:42.480 --> 09:44.680
the country is destined to be ours.

09:45.200 --> 09:46.040
Good!

09:54.000 --> 09:56.440
Before, I said I'd help you
find this woman.

09:57.120 --> 09:59.760
Seems I was meddling.

10:07.960 --> 10:09.000
Brothers!

10:09.080 --> 10:10.280
Follow me to march into the county town!

10:11.160 --> 10:12.600
And find my woman too!

10:12.680 --> 10:13.720
Hyah!

10:23.680 --> 10:26.880
LUO'S PAWNSHOP

10:26.960 --> 10:30.240
LUO'S PAWNSHOP

10:37.960 --> 10:39.360
Let's leave! Move that way!

10:50.760 --> 10:52.440
FAN'S BRAISED MEAT

10:52.520 --> 10:53.600
Get up!

11:17.200 --> 11:17.920
Help!

11:18.000 --> 11:20.320
Help! Help!

11:33.000 --> 11:33.920
Stop!

11:48.440 --> 11:49.280
Don't kill me!

12:17.240 --> 12:21.000
PANCAKE

12:29.000 --> 12:30.480
-Move!
-Hurry!

12:30.560 --> 12:31.920
-Hurry!
-Go!

12:32.000 --> 12:33.520
-Kneel!
-Kneel!

12:33.600 --> 12:34.440
Kneel!

12:37.840 --> 12:40.160
I was told you all know
that pig-slaughtering woman.

12:40.840 --> 12:43.080
Tell me. What's her name?

12:43.160 --> 12:44.960
Where is she?

12:45.720 --> 12:46.800
Tell me,

12:47.680 --> 12:49.080
and you live.

13:05.400 --> 13:06.440
You, speak.

13:08.240 --> 13:09.360
Sir.

13:09.880 --> 13:11.880
I don't know who you're talking about.

13:17.440 --> 13:18.880
Trying to fool me?

13:19.640 --> 13:20.600
Your Highness.

13:21.200 --> 13:23.520
You just became Shisan Niang's boyfriend.

13:23.600 --> 13:25.880
Now you're looking
for another woman already.

13:25.960 --> 13:26.920
Right.

13:27.000 --> 13:29.280
Our big boss has a temper
and holds grudges.

13:29.360 --> 13:31.400
Be careful, your own life is in danger.

13:35.640 --> 13:37.560
I'm not doing this for personal feelings…

13:39.440 --> 13:40.920
but for revenge.

13:58.440 --> 13:59.480
You, speak.

14:04.280 --> 14:05.960
I don't know.

14:19.640 --> 14:21.360
Run!

14:24.880 --> 14:25.880
Run!

14:30.320 --> 14:32.000
Shoot! Shoot! Kill them! Quick!

14:36.200 --> 14:37.320
Run!

14:40.360 --> 14:41.920
One got away. Chase them.

15:24.000 --> 15:25.080
You, speak.

15:27.920 --> 15:29.440
Your granny here

15:30.440 --> 15:32.480
doesn't know!

15:47.960 --> 15:49.160
You'd better…

15:50.440 --> 15:51.920
really not know.

15:54.400 --> 15:55.920
You killed my father.

15:57.000 --> 15:58.360
You killed my mother.

16:00.200 --> 16:02.320
What's the point of me living on alone?

16:04.600 --> 16:06.280
You beast!

16:08.520 --> 16:10.120
If you've got guts, just kill me!

16:11.040 --> 16:12.440
Kill me!

16:17.840 --> 16:19.440
You have more guts than your father does.

16:21.880 --> 16:23.080
Then I'll grant your wish.

16:39.840 --> 16:42.960
You're probably clueless too.

16:43.040 --> 16:45.400
I… I know. I know.

16:45.480 --> 16:49.040
I know, I know!

16:49.120 --> 16:51.320
My Lord, that pig-slaughtering woman
you mentioned…

16:51.400 --> 16:52.960
She's called Fan Changyu.

16:53.040 --> 16:54.640
I know her. Her house is over there.

16:55.320 --> 16:56.800
I can take you there right now.

16:56.880 --> 16:58.560
Spare my life, my Lord!

16:58.640 --> 17:00.120
Enough talking. Alright, alright.
Lead the way.

17:00.720 --> 17:02.080
-You are spared. Get up.
-Okay.

17:10.440 --> 17:12.319
Fan Changyu.

17:14.119 --> 17:16.200
My Lord, it's here.

17:20.079 --> 17:22.960
My Lord, it's right here.

17:23.040 --> 17:24.480
This is Fan Changyu's home.

17:25.000 --> 17:27.359
Are you sure it's here?
Didn't lead us wrong?

17:27.440 --> 17:28.600
I'm sure, so sure.

17:28.680 --> 17:31.360
Right, they raised pigs in the backyard.

17:34.640 --> 17:36.120
You don't believe me?

17:36.200 --> 17:37.680
I'll take you to look right now.

17:52.760 --> 17:55.160
I hate disloyalty the most in my life.

17:55.680 --> 17:57.840
Even sell out their own people.

17:59.240 --> 18:01.320
Dying like that was letting her off easy.

18:02.360 --> 18:03.440
Drag her out and whip the corpse.

20:15.720 --> 20:17.720
How can you be so heartless?

20:17.800 --> 20:18.960
I came looking for you.

20:19.040 --> 20:20.200
Yet you want my life.

20:20.280 --> 20:22.040
I'll show you

20:22.120 --> 20:23.600
what truly being heartless means.

20:23.680 --> 20:25.160
If I die here,

20:25.760 --> 20:27.640
you and the people in the cellar
will have no hope of escaping either.

20:32.680 --> 20:33.920
You let me go,

20:34.600 --> 20:36.000
and I'll spare you
and the people in the cellar.

20:38.480 --> 20:39.800
Why should I believe you?

20:40.320 --> 20:41.520
Your Highness.

20:47.120 --> 20:48.920
How about you just gamble on it?

20:51.520 --> 20:52.480
Your Highness.

20:54.160 --> 20:55.200
Your Highness.

20:56.680 --> 20:57.840
Your Highness, is something wrong?

21:05.520 --> 21:06.360
Your Highness.

21:06.440 --> 21:07.320
Your Highness.

21:10.240 --> 21:11.960
What's going on here?

21:13.720 --> 21:14.600
Your Highness.

21:15.120 --> 21:16.880
So this is the revenge you mentioned?

21:17.680 --> 21:20.800
Isn't it more satisfying this way?

21:20.880 --> 21:22.200
Get lost.

21:22.960 --> 21:24.440
I'm not finished yet.

21:25.880 --> 21:28.240
Alright, go on, please.

21:35.560 --> 21:37.680
If Marquis Wu'an saw this,

21:38.200 --> 21:39.560
wouldn't his heart ache terribly?

21:41.120 --> 21:42.720
What's that got to do with Marquis Wu'an?

21:42.800 --> 21:44.120
What?

21:44.640 --> 21:46.720
You don't have the guts
to admit you're his woman?

21:50.240 --> 21:52.880
MARQUIS WU'AN, YAN ZHENG

21:54.600 --> 21:55.520
Indeed.

21:57.160 --> 21:58.520
I admire Marquis Wu'an

21:58.600 --> 22:00.080
and want to be his woman.

22:00.840 --> 22:02.560
What's that got to do with you?

22:06.120 --> 22:07.880
Then how about you try first?

22:09.120 --> 22:10.880
Who between Marquis Wu'an and me

22:11.680 --> 22:13.600
is better at being tender?

22:18.800 --> 22:19.680
Let's go.

22:31.280 --> 22:32.680
You took me as the hostage.

22:33.200 --> 22:34.880
Of course I have to act convincing.

22:35.800 --> 22:36.920
Otherwise, how can I get you out

22:38.480 --> 22:41.080
and help you hide the fact
that there are people in the cellar?

22:44.240 --> 22:46.040
If your knife goes in two more inches,

22:46.560 --> 22:47.880
and I'm dead,

22:49.240 --> 22:50.120
then what?

22:50.640 --> 22:54.120
-You want to fight a hundred people alone?
-So much nonsense.

22:56.080 --> 22:56.960
Behave.

23:03.680 --> 23:04.960
Second Boss is here.

23:14.640 --> 23:16.480
Second Boss, what's the meaning of this?

23:17.080 --> 23:20.560
You want to take this woman
back to Qingfeng Stronghold?

23:22.840 --> 23:24.760
Finally see one to your liking.

23:26.600 --> 23:28.360
If you want to marry Shisan Niang,

23:28.440 --> 23:30.800
then kill this woman.

23:34.560 --> 23:37.680
Second Boss wants me to stay
with Shisan Niang my whole life?

23:38.200 --> 23:39.800
Only her for life?

23:40.960 --> 23:43.160
Second Boss married four stronghold wives.

23:43.240 --> 23:45.800
The common girls you've taken
are too many to count.

23:45.880 --> 23:47.240
We're all men.

23:48.040 --> 23:50.040
Why demand this of me?

23:52.280 --> 23:53.680
You're not wrong.

23:54.600 --> 23:56.120
But as for my sister's temper,

23:56.680 --> 23:59.720
if she finds out you brought
another woman back,

23:59.800 --> 24:01.400
she'll definitely kill you.

24:02.040 --> 24:03.360
When I return to the stronghold,

24:03.960 --> 24:05.040
I'll have an explanation.

24:06.240 --> 24:07.960
Fine. Let's go.

24:08.560 --> 24:09.400
Back to the stronghold.

24:16.120 --> 24:17.240
Get on the horse, quickly.

24:27.720 --> 24:28.720
Still this move?

24:39.840 --> 24:40.960
Guards!

24:42.800 --> 24:43.960
The Prince is being held hostage!

24:44.040 --> 24:45.560
Go save the Prince!

24:45.640 --> 24:47.440
You bunch of fools!

24:51.200 --> 24:52.880
I must draw the bandits away,

24:52.960 --> 24:54.320
-so Ning and the others are safe.
-Let go!

25:01.480 --> 25:02.880
-Scoundrels, come chase me!
-Catch her!

25:02.960 --> 25:03.640
-Catch her!
-Hyah!

25:04.600 --> 25:06.520
-Get her now!
-Your Highness, wake up!

25:06.600 --> 25:07.960
-Halt!
-Stop!

25:08.040 --> 25:09.080
Hey you!

25:09.160 --> 25:10.400
Halt!

25:10.480 --> 25:11.440
Don't run!

25:11.520 --> 25:12.440
-Catch her!
-Stop now!

25:13.320 --> 25:14.560
The Prince's woman ran away!

25:14.640 --> 25:16.600
-More men! Follow me!
-Hurry!

25:16.680 --> 25:18.360
-Halt!
-Go after her!

25:21.120 --> 25:22.440
Granny, I'm hungry.

25:23.320 --> 25:25.040
Don't make a sound. Wait a bit longer.

25:25.560 --> 25:28.000
In a little while, Granny
will heat up dumplings for you.

25:43.000 --> 25:44.320
Sister.

25:45.480 --> 25:46.640
Sister.

25:49.000 --> 25:50.080
Sister.

25:50.160 --> 25:51.280
Sister.

25:52.520 --> 25:53.560
Sister.

25:55.160 --> 25:56.720
Sister.

25:59.160 --> 26:00.200
Sister.

26:01.880 --> 26:04.640
Sister, where are you?

26:05.160 --> 26:06.800
Sister.

26:09.480 --> 26:12.520
Sister, where are you?

26:15.280 --> 26:17.480
Sister, where are you?

26:19.240 --> 26:20.160
Over there.

26:20.240 --> 26:21.160
Go look over there.

26:22.440 --> 26:23.400
There, there.

26:26.640 --> 26:28.240
Why haven't I seen Changning?

26:28.760 --> 26:29.640
Changning has asthma.

26:29.720 --> 26:32.440
She can't stay in this cellar for long.

26:32.520 --> 26:34.640
Her sister hid her in a safe place.

26:35.680 --> 26:36.920
I'll go up and look.

26:57.040 --> 26:57.920
Ning.

26:59.200 --> 27:00.160
Ning.

27:01.400 --> 27:02.360
Ning.

27:04.760 --> 27:06.200
LIN'AN

28:29.600 --> 28:30.720
Run!

28:30.800 --> 28:32.000
Why aren't you running?

28:34.200 --> 28:35.520
Get her!

28:56.640 --> 28:57.760
Shoot her!

29:28.160 --> 29:29.360
Second Boss!

29:29.440 --> 29:30.440
Second Boss!

29:30.520 --> 29:31.520
Outrageous!

29:31.600 --> 29:33.720
Avenge Second Boss! Go after her!

29:56.040 --> 29:57.600
Heard you were in danger at the front.

29:58.120 --> 29:59.440
Although Chancellor said nothing,

29:59.520 --> 30:00.640
he was deeply worried

30:00.720 --> 30:02.040
and could‘t sleep day or night.

30:02.120 --> 30:04.680
Now, learning you've recovered
and escaped danger,

30:04.760 --> 30:06.480
he specially ordered me to visit you.

30:07.000 --> 30:08.240
Never thought I'd meet you halfway.

30:08.320 --> 30:09.880
Thank Uncle for his concern.

30:10.440 --> 30:12.760
Also, please tell Uncle for me.

30:13.280 --> 30:15.480
I'm hard to kill and manage to live on.

30:16.840 --> 30:19.800
I'm afraid the one who tried to harm me

30:20.400 --> 30:21.720
can't eat or sleep soundly now.

30:24.520 --> 30:26.080
We've been fellow disciples
for many years.

30:26.160 --> 30:27.960
I should have taken care of you.

30:28.040 --> 30:29.080
Unfortunately,

30:30.120 --> 30:32.000
I am constrained too.

30:33.320 --> 30:34.200
Doesn't matter.

30:34.280 --> 30:37.880
You are by Chancellor's side.

30:38.400 --> 30:41.080
I am glad that your heart is with me.

30:44.520 --> 30:47.560
Now, regarding Lucheng,
what are your plans?

30:48.080 --> 30:49.280
What plans?

30:49.800 --> 30:51.360
My wounds aren't healed.

30:51.440 --> 30:53.600
Lucheng has General He Jingyuan
holding the fort.

30:54.440 --> 30:57.200
Originally, Wei Xuan could have
supervised the army here.

30:57.280 --> 30:58.480
I could have slacked off a bit.

30:59.000 --> 31:01.120
But then this fellow suddenly
returned to the capital.

31:01.840 --> 31:02.680
Right now,

31:02.760 --> 31:05.720
I can only protect the soldiers under me,
keep them safe and sound.

31:06.320 --> 31:09.400
Only then do we have the strength
to take revenge and wipe away disgrace.

31:14.520 --> 31:15.800
Marquis.

31:15.880 --> 31:17.760
Haidongqing flew back from Lin'an.

31:22.720 --> 31:23.640
Lin'an?

31:26.240 --> 31:27.800
Assemble a hundred Blood-Clad Cavalry.
Follow me to Lin'an.

31:27.880 --> 31:28.720
Yes.

31:32.880 --> 31:34.000
Search the place!

31:49.320 --> 31:51.680
Hu, does your tooth still hurt?

31:51.760 --> 31:53.440
It stopped hurting long ago.

31:59.480 --> 32:00.920
Has this room been searched?

32:01.560 --> 32:02.920
Things inside are such a mess.

32:03.000 --> 32:04.480
It must have been searched.

32:05.040 --> 32:07.000
No. This one hasn't been searched.

32:07.080 --> 32:08.120
Go in and search.

32:10.520 --> 32:11.440
Hu.

32:12.120 --> 32:14.360
-The dumplings are covered on the stove.
-Check over there.

32:14.440 --> 32:15.920
-Okay.
-Heat five at a time.

32:16.000 --> 32:17.440
-No one here.
-Don't eat too many.

32:18.640 --> 32:20.000
-Six is okay too.
-The front room?

32:20.080 --> 32:22.160
-Your stomach will hurt if you overeat.
-Move.

32:23.120 --> 32:24.200
Did you search inside?

32:24.280 --> 32:27.720
The cured meat in the yard
is enough to eat until the snow melts.

32:27.800 --> 32:29.680
Feed the chickens with grain.

32:30.200 --> 32:31.560
When the chickens lay eggs,

32:31.640 --> 32:33.160
don't eat them all.

32:35.280 --> 32:36.480
As long as there are eggs,

32:37.160 --> 32:38.440
you can hatch chicks.

32:38.960 --> 32:39.800
Over there.

32:40.960 --> 32:43.200
-If you have eggs, you won't go hungry.
-No one there.

32:44.480 --> 32:46.120
Wait for your brother to return.

32:49.200 --> 32:50.360
Go search there.

32:55.880 --> 32:58.320
Before dawn, absolutely do not go out.

33:57.800 --> 33:58.560
Who is that?

33:59.240 --> 34:00.160
Who is that?

34:10.560 --> 34:12.000
You bunch of bastards!

34:12.080 --> 34:13.960
I'll fight you to the death!

34:15.280 --> 34:16.560
I'll fight you to the death!

34:20.239 --> 34:21.520
I, an old woman alone,

34:22.120 --> 34:23.320
with no sons or daughters,

34:23.960 --> 34:25.280
I'm not afraid of you.

34:25.360 --> 34:29.120
You bunch, born but not raised!

34:29.719 --> 34:30.920
You beasts!

34:42.719 --> 34:44.080
Dead old hag!

34:44.159 --> 34:45.639
Foul-mouthed.

34:45.719 --> 34:46.920
Nagging.

34:47.000 --> 34:49.000
Serves you right. No one to send you off.

35:37.760 --> 35:40.560
Young lady, nowhere to run now?

35:41.080 --> 35:42.160
Yield to me.

35:46.040 --> 35:47.800
I'm much better than Marquis Wu'an.

35:48.520 --> 35:51.040
Follow me, and I'll spare your life.

35:59.080 --> 36:00.040
Take a step back,

36:01.080 --> 36:02.760
and you'll die without a burial place.

36:25.800 --> 36:26.640
Report!

36:26.720 --> 36:27.840
Report!

36:27.920 --> 36:28.760
Report!

36:29.320 --> 36:31.720
Your Highness,
our stronghold was slaughtered.

36:32.400 --> 36:33.240
Who did it?

36:33.320 --> 36:35.200
People who escaped the stronghold said

36:35.720 --> 36:37.160
it was Marquis Wu'an's Blood-Clad Cavalry.

36:37.240 --> 36:39.080
A full hundred men.

36:41.200 --> 36:42.360
So it's him.

36:42.440 --> 36:44.400
A hundred Blood-Clad Cavalry Guards…

36:44.920 --> 36:46.960
Enough for taking a city.

36:48.000 --> 36:49.600
Let alone a small Qingfeng Stronghold.

36:55.720 --> 36:56.720
QINGFENG STRONGHOLD

37:08.040 --> 37:09.880
Marquis, the stronghold
has been thoroughly searched.

37:09.960 --> 37:10.920
Mrs. Fan was not found,

37:11.000 --> 37:12.640
nor the people from Lin'an Town.

37:12.720 --> 37:13.880
People in Lin'an Town
were also slaughtered.

37:13.960 --> 37:14.920
We saved some people,

37:15.000 --> 37:16.120
but Mrs. Fan is not there.

37:16.640 --> 37:17.960
We also searched Xigu Alley.

37:18.040 --> 37:19.800
No trace of Mrs. Fan or Changning.

37:39.280 --> 37:41.280
QINGFENG STRONGHOLD

37:50.480 --> 37:51.400
Go find her.

37:55.880 --> 37:56.720
Go.

39:28.240 --> 39:29.680
Marquis, let me help.

39:51.560 --> 39:52.480
Blood-Clad Cavalry.

39:52.560 --> 39:53.400
Yes.

39:53.480 --> 39:54.920
Find a place to shelter and warm up.

39:55.680 --> 39:56.520
Yes.

40:05.560 --> 40:07.360
Marquis, let us carry her.

40:08.000 --> 40:08.880
Who are you to do that?

40:08.960 --> 40:10.960
Hang the corpses of bandits
on the city tower.

40:11.040 --> 40:12.040
Gut them.

40:12.120 --> 40:13.280
Leave the bodies exposed for three days.

40:14.160 --> 40:15.000
-Yes.
-Yes.

40:56.680 --> 40:57.520
Changyu.

40:58.040 --> 40:59.280
Changyu.

41:13.120 --> 41:14.000
Changyu.

41:23.000 --> 41:25.480
Why aren't you the Fan Changyu I know?

41:26.160 --> 41:28.080
That person who was always warm.

41:29.360 --> 41:31.640
Why is your body now ice-cold?

41:43.440 --> 41:44.360
Changyu.

41:44.880 --> 41:45.720
Changyu.

41:46.520 --> 41:48.200
I won't let anything happen to you.

41:49.080 --> 41:49.920
Changyu.

41:51.960 --> 41:52.960
Changyu.

42:14.080 --> 42:17.040
This is evil cold entering the body.

42:18.280 --> 42:20.320
Pulse is faint.

42:21.480 --> 42:24.080
Already reached a life-threatening pass.

42:25.360 --> 42:28.200
Must scrape her to activate
blood circulation.

42:29.240 --> 42:31.280
Unblock the meridians.

42:32.400 --> 42:35.440
Dispel the wind-cold from her body.

42:35.520 --> 42:36.200
CINNABAR

42:36.280 --> 42:38.120
MEDICINE

42:43.800 --> 42:44.800
Madam.

42:45.840 --> 42:46.840
You know medicine?

42:47.720 --> 42:48.960
A little.

42:49.040 --> 42:50.680
I beg you, save her life.

42:51.440 --> 42:53.480
It's just a pity,

42:53.560 --> 42:57.600
my son and daughter-in-law
went to town to sell medicine.

42:58.280 --> 43:00.960
I'm a blind old woman.

43:02.720 --> 43:05.960
Is there a woman among you

43:06.040 --> 43:07.720
who can help with the scraping?

43:11.000 --> 43:12.560
I am her husband.

43:13.160 --> 43:14.120
I can do it.

46:08.000 --> 46:11.680
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:11.760 --> 46:12.640
Subtitle translation by: Peng Peng
